trans-unit.source: Iterates over all preceding nodes according to the XPath preceding axis rules, and returns nodes in reverse document order without duplicates.
trans-unit.target: 循环访问所有前面的节点，根据 XPath 前面的轴规则，并以没有重复项的反向文档顺序返回节点。

trans-unit.source: The XPath preceding axis rules specify that ancestors are not included, even though they precede the starting node in document order.
trans-unit.target: XPath 前面的轴规则指定上级不包括在内，即使它们位于起始节点之前按文档顺序。

trans-unit.source: The node from which you start traversing ancestors.
trans-unit.target: 从其开始遍历祖先节点。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"></xref> class, which enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: 实例<xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XmlNavigatorFilter"></xref>类，该类可用于筛选依据的名称的节点。

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 导航器更改仅在状态<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>方法已返回`true`。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next preceding node in reverse document order.
trans-unit.target: 将迭代器定位在按反向文档顺序到下一步前面的节点上。

trans-unit.source: If the iterator was set to the next preceding node, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果迭代器已设置为下一步前面的节点，MoveNext 方法会设置<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A>属性设置为当前结果导航器; 否则为<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A>属性保持不变。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingIterator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the iterator was set to the next preceding node; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果迭代器设置为下一步前面的节点;否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。
